Alignment for the item's [text](Text_%28GUI_item_property%29 "Text (GUI item property)") , when available: 0 is for left alignment, 1 for center alignment, and 2 for right aligment.

The value of this property cannot be changed at runtime.

Syntax
------

    textalign alignment

Default value
-------------

    0

Example(s)
----------

    textalign 1

